        ## Usage
        
        For detailed usage, see the tests
        
        ```python
        
        from drf_keyvalue.keyvalue import get_client
        
        import redis
        redis.StrictRedis(host='localhost', port=6379, db=0)
        
        client = get_client('keyvalue.backends.RedisBackend', connection)
        
        ```
        
